Class MockBundleContextBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.steria.osgi.mocks.MockBundleContextBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.osgi.framework.BundleContext, org.osgi.framework.BundleReference
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockBundleContext

    public class MockBundleContextBase
extends Object
implements org.osgi.framework.BundleContext
    Default implementations for all methods of BundleContext. The actual mock class inherits this class, and only needs replace those methods needed by the tests.

    Steinar Bang
